item.title: LiKe BuTTeR: 'Solo Build! (The Division) 201+ Sustain Nomad Build'
item.description:
Here is my build that I put together for the 201+ bracket in order to survive npcs as a solo player. Keep in mind, even though this is not a solid build for pvp, you can still pvp with it. I used it yesterday and was doing fine. Also having self preserved on your primary will help you sustain as well. Let me know what you guys think of the build! Drop a LIKE if you enjoyed! Thank you!

item.title: LiKe BuTTeR: 'THE DREAM DROP! (The Division) 204 MP7'
item.description:
This has to be one of the best drops I have ever gotten in the Dark Zone. This is a 204 MP7 with Swift, Brutal, & Deadly. It has 10.3k base damage and 24% Crit Chance. Having 180k dps with a solo Nomad and FInal Measure tank build. I can only imagine what this is going to output with 3 striker, 2 sentry's. Be sure to drop the video a LIKE if you enjoyed! Thank you!
